1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode Four=

11
00:00:51,439 --> 00:00:52,679
Get down here.

12
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,240
Wash it off.

13
00:01:13,799 --> 00:01:15,400
You met him today.

14
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:16,560
How did it go?

15
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:25,159
Your Highness.

16
00:01:25,239 --> 00:01:26,879
A fake is still a fake.

17
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,799
Besides your appearance,

18
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:32,319
you're no match for her in grace or wit.

19
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,439
That's enough for today.

20
00:01:34,959 --> 00:01:37,040
Guard, see her out.

21
00:01:37,879 --> 00:01:40,000
I failed today. I'm sorry.

22
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:42,040
Princess Mei Lin, this way, please.

23
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,040
Please show mercy, Your Highness.

24
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,560
Give me one more chance.

25
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:48,640
One more chance?

26
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:54,239
I don't have that much patience.

27
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,280
If you fail again

28
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:59,000
you will die from poison.

29
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:09,000
I'm willing to do whatever it takes.

30
00:02:21,439 --> 00:02:24,319
Is that all you learned
in the Shadow Bureau?

31
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:29,919
Seems I'll have to teach you myself.

32
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,599
Things delivered to your doorstep?

33
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,039
Men only find them cheap.

34
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:38,319
Keep him at a distance.

35
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:39,400
Make him restless.

36
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:42,159
Yet he doesn't even
have a chance to touch you.

37
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,039
How?

38
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,759
Make tea.

39
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,360
(My mother was a master
of the tea ceremony.)

40
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,879
(And Murong Xuanlie)

41
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:59,479
(used to hide behind the rocks
in the Imperial Garden)

42
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,400
(just to watch her make tea.)

43
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,360
What are you doing here?

44
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,840
If I disturbed you, Your Highness

45
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:19,080
I'm leaving now.

46
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,479
Since you've made tea

47
00:03:21,639 --> 00:03:23,520
why not let me taste it?

48
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:35,439
Unbrace yourself.

49
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:38,800
Be gentle. Be steady.

50
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:41,080
Watch me.

51
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,080
Remember

52
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:47,280
you are not seducing your enemy.

53
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,599
You are seducing a man.

54
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:59,479
(Use the steam well when you brew.)

55
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:12,159
Your Highness, please.

56
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:15,599
(When offering tea,
let your fingers linger.)

57
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,399
(A touch, then retreat.)

58
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,800
(Just enough to tempt.)

59
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:28,560
(Remember, make him feel
he's about to have you,)

60
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,680
(yet doubt if he ever will.)

61
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:36,120
You've tasted the tea, Your Highness.

62
00:04:36,759 --> 00:04:39,040
I really should go now.

63
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:51,399
Your Highness,
it was a misunderstanding before.

64
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:54,079
I never meant to be anyone's substitute.

65
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:56,519
So I won't bother you any longer.

66
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:03,279
Stop pretending.

67
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:05,720
Isn't this all just to win me over?

68
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,199
As you wish.

69
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,399
I grant you the position
of Secondary Consort

70
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:13,279
and will marry you with full honor.

71
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:16,240
Does that satisfy you?

72
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:18,560
Your Highness.

73
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,240
In quite the mood today, aren't you?

74
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,759
Prince Xuanlie!

75
00:05:55,220 --> 00:05:57,180
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

76
00:05:57,430 --> 00:06:00,400
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

77
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:03,740
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

78
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:07,420
ظآزLike blossoms that refuse to fadeظآز

79
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:11,220
ظآزIt asks no right or wrongظآز

80
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:14,220
ظآزNor fears the turning of fateظآز

81
00:06:15,340 --> 00:06:16,940
ظآزA trace of spring on the windظآز

82
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:19,580
ظآزA whisper of a broken heartظآز

83
00:06:21,460 --> 00:06:23,540
ظآزA farewell song unfoldsظآز

84
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:26,740
ظآزCarrying every sorrow within itظآز

85
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:29,180
ظآزKarma weaves its endless threadظآز

86
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:33,140
ظآزAnd I would follow you
without turning backظآز

87
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:36,620
ظآزLife and death become
nothing sharp or finalظآز

88
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:40,020
ظآزLove and hate are carried away
on the breezeظآز

89
00:06:40,620 --> 00:06:42,820
ظآزBefore freedom is ever reachedظآز

90
00:06:42,820 --> 00:06:45,860
ظآزOne must first dissolve into tearsظآز

91
00:06:46,460 --> 00:06:49,540
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
